      <title>劳埃德银行 (Lloyds) 向罗思西 (Rothesay) 出售价值 60 亿英镑的苏格兰寡妇年金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/lloyds-sells-6-billion-of-scottish-widows-annuities-to-rothesay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳埃德银行集团 (Lloyds Banking Group Plc) 将从其苏格兰寡妇子公司 (Scottish Widows) 中将 60 亿英镑（合 76.7 亿美元）的大宗年金投资组合出售给养老保险专业公司 Rothesay Life Plc。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/lloyds-sells-6-billion-of-scottish-widows-annuities-to-rothesay</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为了节省成本，壳牌将削减交易团队约 20% 的职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/shell-to-cut-about-20-of-jobs-in-deals-team-amid-push-for-cost-savings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，壳牌公司将在其交易团队中裁减至少 20% 的职位，因为该公司将继续重组其业务部门以降低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/shell-to-cut-about-20-of-jobs-in-deals-team-amid-push-for-cost-savings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:21:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
